        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Passion Melts Ice",
        "Client": "Dame Luchika",
        "Description": "I apologize if my behavior can be\r\na bit much out in the field, but\r\nI\u0027m rather passionate about my\r\nprofession. And why shouldn\u0027t\r\nI be? Perhaps we can drown out\r\nthe sound of my critics with\r\na few well-placed blasts, yes?",
        "Target": "Hunt an Aurora Somnacanth",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "La flamme de la passion",
        "Client": "Dame Luchika",
        "Description": "J\u0027aimerais que tu m\u0027aides pour\r\nune qu\u00EAte dans l\u0027Archipel de\r\nglace. J\u0027ai tendance \u00E0 \u00EAtre un\r\npeu trop obstin\u00E9e \u00E0 la chasse,\r\nmais avec la Flamme \u00E0 mes\r\nc\u00F4t\u00E9s, je devrais m\u0027en sortir.\r\nAllons-y !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Somnacanth aurore",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Passione scioglighiaccio",
        "Client": "Dama Luchika",
        "Description": "Vorrei che venissi con me\r\nper una missione alle Isole\r\nghiacciate. So che durante la\r\ncaccia mi lascio coinvolgere\r\ntroppo, sono troppo risoluta,\r\nma con l\u0027Audace torner\u00F2 tutta\r\nd\u0027un pezzo. Partiamo subito!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Somnacanth fulgido",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Leidenschaft bricht das Eis",
        "Client": "Luchika",
        "Description": "Ich entschuldige mich, wenn\r\nmein Verhalten ein bisschen\r\nviel sein kann, aber ich bin\r\nleidenschaftlich in meinem\r\nBeruf. Warum auch nicht?\r\nVielleicht k\u00F6nnen wir den\r\nKlang meiner Kritiker mit ein\r\npaar guten Treffern \u00FCbert\u00F6nen?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Auroracanth.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Una pasi\u00F3n que te derrite",
        "Client": "Luchika",
        "Description": "Te pido disculpas si mi\r\nentusiasmo resulta excesivo,\r\npero siento una gran pasi\u00F3n por\r\nmi trabajo. \u00BFPor qu\u00E9 no deber\u00EDa?\r\nQuiz\u00E1 podamos silenciar el ruido\r\nde mis detractores con unos\r\nbuenos disparos, \u00BFno?",
        "Target": "Caza un Somnacanth Aurora",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0421\u0442\u0440\u0430\u0441\u0442\u044C \u0440\u0430\u0441\u0442\u043E\u043F\u0438\u0442 \u043B\u0435\u0434",
